<l>in non-case-relation as in case-relation <foreign xml:lang="ta">sandhi.</foreign><note
              place="foot">i.e. the noun <foreign xml:lang="ta">eṇ</foreign> ' sesame seed ' may have its <foreign xml:lang="ta">-ṇ</foreign> assimilated to <foreign
